### Health Check Server
GET http://localhost:5000/

### ==========================================
### POSTS ROUTES
### ==========================================

### 1. Analyze and save a new post (Emergency Example)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/posts/analyze
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "text": "URGENT: Major fire outbreak at the downtown warehouse! People are trapped!",
    "source": "twitter"
}

### 1b. Analyze and save a new post (Non-Emergency Example)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/posts/analyze
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "text": "The pothole on 5th avenue is really annoying. Someone should fix it eventually.",
    "source": "facebook"
}

### 2. Get all posts
GET http://localhost:5000/api/posts

### 3. Get posts filtered by severity and topic
GET http://localhost:5000/api/posts?severity=Critical&topic=Public%20Safety

### 4. Get only CRITICAL posts (dedicated route)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/posts/critical

### 5. Mark a post as resolved
# -> Note: Replace 'YOUR_DOCUMENT_ID_HERE' with an actual _id from the GET /api/posts request
PATCH http://localhost:5000/api/posts/YOUR_DOCUMENT_ID_HERE/resolve
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "adminNotes": "Forwarded this issue to the local authorities for immediate action."
}

### ==========================================
### AUTHENTICATION ROUTES
### ==========================================

### 6. Register First Admin
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Admin Tester",
    "email": "admin@example.com",
    "password": "Password123"
}

### 7. Login to get JWT Token
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "admin@example.com",
    "password": "Password123"
}

### ==========================================
### BULK DATASET UPLOAD
### ==========================================

### 8. Upload a batch of 5 posts
### Make sure to copy the token from the Login request and replace YOUR_TOKEN_HERE below!
POST http://localhost:5000/api/upload/dataset
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
    "dataset": [
        {
            "text": "The downtown intersection has a completely busted traffic light. It's been broken for 3 days.",
            "source": "twitter"
        },
        {
            "text": "I am so completely exhausted with everything, I don't see the point in living anymore.",
            "source": "facebook"
        },
        {
            "text": "There's a massive car crash on I-95, multiple lanes are completely blocked!",
            "source": "reddit"
        },
        {
            "text": "Bro this internet lag is unbearable, I literally want to murder my router.",
            "source": "twitter"
        },
        {
            "text": "The new park that the city built is absolutely beautiful! Having a great day here.",
            "source": "instagram"
        }
    ]
}

### ==========================================
### DASHBOARD & ANALYSIS ROUTES
### ==========================================

### 9. Get aggregate Dashboard Stats
GET http://localhost:5000/api/dashboard/stats

### 10. Analysis Placeholder route
GET http://localhost:5000/api/analysis
